results.title: Kitchen Home Decor SmartScreen Stencil - Reusable, Self adhesive - Canvas, Cards, Glass, Ceramic, Walls, Fabric, Wood, Plastic, Metal, Clay
results.description:
Our smart silkscreen stencils are very versatile, self-adhesive, yet easily adjustable AND reusable. Perfect for adding that home-made touch effortlessly. No previous experience required.

This stencil is available in three sizes: A4, A5, and A6 - the image on the stencil is smaller. Note that only the large A4 stencil set has both quotes!
Quote sizes are as followed: 
A4 stencil set        = Home quote is 26.4 cm by 9.8 cm | 10.39" by 3.86"; 
                                   Kitchen quote is 26.4 cm by 7.9 cm | 10.39" by 3.11".
A5 Home quote    = 20 cm by 7.4 cm | 7.87" by 2.91".
A5(K) Kitchen quote = 20 cm by 6 cm | 7.87" by 2.36".
A6 Home quote    = 11.2 cm by 4.2 cm | 4.41" by 1.65".
A6(K) Kitchen quote = 11.2 cm by 3.4 cm | 4.41" by 1.34".
All images, except for the large stencil, are placed on an A4 size background to give you a reference for size. The large stencil is 12" by 10", which is slightly larger than an A4 sheet.
Note: the red and grey text in the images is added to protect copyright and is NOT part of the actual stencil.

ALL SURFACE OR FABRIC/WOOD?  

All Surface - The original blue stencil can be used on almost any type of surface, provided it is clean and smooth. It can be used on paper, cardboard, canvas, metal, clay (polymer), glass, ceramics, walls, plastic, tile, wood (sand first for best results), fabric, etc. However, if you plan on stenciling fabric or rough wood only, then order the Fabric/Wood one.

Fabric/Wood - The upgraded purple stencil is specifically developed for stenciling on fabric or rough wood. This stencil is slightly sturdier, a lot stickier, yet still flexible and reusable. Be sure to order the Fabric/Wood stencil in your preferred size if you're only planning on using it on fabric or rough wood.


NEED A PERSONALIZED STENCIL?

Besides stencils like these, we also make custom stencils. Go to our "Order Custom Stencil" category and click. 
Order your preferred size stencil and send us your design and preferred measurements in a private message through Etsy. 
Not sure which about the size or detail? Just contact us before you order and we will answer any questions you might have.

HOW TO USE YOUR NEW STENCIL:

1. First things first: we HIGHLY recommend turning your stencil over and writing something on the back of the foil the stencil is stuck on with a permanent marker. It doesn't matter what it says, but we write the word "NO" on it. This is to remind you NOT to stick the stencil back onto this side after use. If you do accidentally stick it back onto the wrong side of the clear foil your stencil will get stuck to it. I've done this a few times by accident, try soaking your stuck stencil and carefully peeling it off the foil, trying not to stretch it.
2. Now that you've written on the back of the foil, peel the stencil off it and stick it to a surface of your choice, be it ceramics, fabric, wood, glass, canvas, etc; flat or curved. Apply some pressure to make it stick and avoid getting air bubbles. 
3. Now apply a thin layer of water-based paint evenly over the top with a squeegee or old credit card. A brush can be used, but using strokes only, no dabbing, as bristles may damage small details on the stencil. 
4. Take off the stencil and your print is done! 
5. Make sure to rinse the stencil carefully straight after use to remove any leftover paint before this dries. We do this under running water, you can gently rub the front of your stencil to remove any paint, but do not rub the backside, simple running water should do the trick. Don't use any scrubbing tools or paint remover items as this may ruin your stencil. 
6. Shake off any excess water and place the stencil upside down on a flat surface (like your kitchen counter). Stick it the foil back on with the writing facing you. Apply some pressure and remove any air bubbles. Dab off any excess water, flip it over and let it dry. Store it out of sunlight and reuse! 
Feel free to contact us if you have any questions.

results.description: This item is a handmade sticker. It was drawn in procreate, then printed on adhesive paper, and lastly, cut out by a silhouette cameo. Everything was done by hand. The item features the words 'live laugh love' written in blue marble. Outside of the words it is black and around that there is a thin white boarder. On the back of the product there is a thin sheet of paper which you will peal off using the cut marks. Please enjoy the live laugh love sticker!

results.title: Live Laugh Love Heart Earrings:  Quinceanera, Sweet Sixteen, Anniversary, BFF, Girlfriend, Sweetheart, Mother, Daughter, Valentine gift
results.description:
I wrote a letter to my love. . . and didn't have to say a word.  Perfect for Valentines Day these Live, Laugh, Love earrings spell it out in a happy combination of fonts and heart symbols.  Whether they're for a sweetheart, girlfriend, mom or yourself, they send out "love" messages as they flutter about like wind chimes on a breezy day.   Light in weight for their size, these shields swing freely below a combination of 2mm hematite beads and 8mm, Rose Gold, Swarovski, crystal rounds.  Swarovski's Rose Gold "color" is the combination of a dark grey crystal with a metallic coating on one side that creates a molten, special effect (picture 2).  Each sterling silver, dome-shaped disc has a brushed matte finish, measures 15/16" across and is printed with words which are impressed and burnished into the surface.  The earrings measures 2-1/8" from the top of the leverback earwire to the bottom of the disc.  All hardware is sterling silver.  CLEAN WITH A SILVER POLISHING CLOTH ONLY (liquid cleaners will remove the black finish on the fonts--ask me how I know this).
SWAROVSKI AUSTRIAN CRYSTAL is still the finest quality, lead crystal made today.  It contains a minimum of 32%PbO, making the crystal optically very pure.  Each crystal is faceted with tremendous precision, forming beautiful light-reflecting prisms.  Brilliant colors-coatings are added creating pendants, stone, and beads of dazzling beauty in a variety of shapes and sizes.
